items.title: FII activity, India-US trade deal among 5 key cues that could set the tone for D-St this week
items.description: Key factors will shape the stock market this week. Domestic data releases like WPI inflation and trade balance are expected. Progress on the India-US trade deal is also a focus. Technical indicators suggest Nifty needs to hold support levels. FII selling continues, while DII buying provides some stability. Currency movements will also be watched closely.

items.title: Fresh delivery: Swiggy raises Rs 10,000 cr via QIP
items.description: In a significant step towards enhancing its market position, food delivery giant Swiggy has raised Rs 10,000 crore through a savvy institutional placement. This capital injection is poised to strengthen its fundamental operations and propel the growth trajectory of Instamart, its rapid commerce division.
